Name: Galactic Gummies
Short description: Embark on a cosmic journey with Galactic Gummies! Whether you're aiming for a subtle microdose by indulging in half a piece or seeking a livelier adventure with a full gummy, these treats adapt to your desired experience. Embrace the mantra of "less is more," let your intuition guide you, and remember, the cosmic delights are in your control – a bite at a time. Each package comes with 8 gummies.

Whether you're aiming for a subtle microdose by indulging in half a piece or seeking a livelier adventure with a full gummy, these treats adapt to your desired experience. Embrace the mantra of "less is more", let your intuition guide you, and remember, the cosmic delights are in your control – a bite at a time. Each package comes with 8 gummies. Serving Size 1/2 piece (100mg) - micro-dose 1 Piece (200mg) - happy 2 Piece (400mg) - giggly Start small, you can eat more later Ingredients Organic cane sugar, organic tapioca syrup, grass-fed gelatin, sorbitol, citric acid, natural flavorings, natural dyes, organic whole fruiting PE6 magic mushroom body (Gluten free) FAQ How does psilocybin work? Psilocybin primarily affects the brain's serotonin receptors, leading to altered perception, mood, and cognition. It promotes increased synaptic connectivity in the brain, potentially influencing emotional and cognitive processes. How do I start micro-dosing? To start micro-dosing, research safe dosages, find a reliable source of psilocybin, create a dosing schedule, and monitor your experiences closely. It's essential to begin with a low dose and be aware of your mental and physical state. What are the benefits of psilocybin micro-dosing? Potential benefits of psilocybin micro-dosing include enhanced mood, increased creativity, reduced anxiety and depression, and improved focus and productivity. Individual experiences may vary.

Name: Cosmic Caramels
Short description: Elevate your taste experience with Cosmic Caramels, infused with enchanting magic mushrooms. Handcrafted with intention & love, each caramel holds a 2,000mg dose, inviting subtle micro-dosing or profound journeys. Savor velvety caramel, set intentions, inhale positivity, and embark on transformative passages guided by nature's mystique. Transcend the ordinary, indulge in the extraordinary, and unlock flavor and exploration with every bite. Each package comes with 2 caramel bars.
